  m_text: "Team Nitemare:\r\n\r\n-Sunny-\r\nteam lead, level design, grass expert\r\n\r\n\r\n-Daniel
    C-\r\nprogramming, systems design, fixing things with a hammer\r\n\r\n\r\n-Duncan-\r\nlevel
    design, UI, dialogue, audio, programming, hero to us all\r\n\r\n\r\n-Luis-\r\nlevel
    design, modeling\r\n\r\nMusic: \r\n\r\nThe Music Class\r\n\r\nFreesounds.org\r\n\r\nStudent
    Assets:\r\n\r\n-Ian-\r\nsledgehammer model\r\n\r\nFree Unity Store Assets: \r\nQuirky
    Animals Series - Omaburats Studio\r\nLiving Birds - Dinopunch\r\nDialogue system
    Ink by Inkle\r\nMess Maker\r\nModern ArchViz: Sea View\r\nFarland Skies - Borodar\r\nApartment
    Kit\r\nFurniture Mega Pack\r\nSimple Low Poly Nature Pack - Clouds\r\n3D Ground
    Platforms | Platform Terrain Set | Floating Islands\r\nParticle pack\r\nRain
    particles\r\nURP Stylized Water Shader - Proto Series\r\nClick to Add\r\n3D set
    of stylized nature - GHIBLI style\r\nFrom Flying toy:\r\nCartoon_Texture_Pack
    - Grass, Fantasy Skybox FREE - Panoramics, Zacxophone - Birds\r\n\r\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\r\n-\r\nThank
    you for playing our game\n-\r\n"
